# Copy to .env and fill in. .env is git-ignored — NEVER commit a real key.
#
# Private key of a funded account on the target network. Used by
# hardhat.config.ts (configVariable) for `--network ritual` deploys.
# Must control a chain-1979 account with testnet ETH.
DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY=0xYOUR_TESTNET_PRIVATE_KEY

# Optional: Sepolia deploys (the starter's example network).
# SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.infura.io/v3/YOUR_KEY
# SEPOLIA_PRIVATE_KEY=0xYOUR_TESTNET_PRIVATE_KEY
